body:
### ODUWSDL GitHub Organization.
[ODU WS-DL](https://ws-dl.cs.odu.edu/) is a computer science research laboratory at [Old Dominion University](http://odu.edu/) in Norfolk, Virginia that specializes in research in web science and digital libraries, as well as sub-fields of information visualization and digital preservation, among many other related topic areas. 

### Our Projects
currently under construction


### About Us
For more information about us, please visit our [website](https://ws-dl.cs.odu.edu). 

We also have a [blog](http://ws-dl.blogspot.com), were we post about the groups activities and topics we find especially interesting.

You can also find us on Twitter [@WebSciDL](https://twitter.com/WebSciDL).
